# Codebase-Memory — Mandatory

MCP: `codebase-memory-mcp` or `user-codebase-memory-mcp`.

## Tool order

| Need | Tool |
|------|------|
| Structure / routes | `get_architecture` |
| Symbol by name | `search_graph` |
| Concept / meaning | `search_graph` + `semantic_query` |
| String / error text | `search_code` |
| Callers / impact | `trace_path` |
| Symbol body | `get_code_snippet` |
| Diff blast radius | `detect_changes` |

**Never** start with Grep/Glob for source. Global hook blocks most source greps.

## New repo

```
index_status → index_repository(repo_path, mode=full, persistence=true)
```

If search is stale after big refactors: re-index, then retry MCP before Grep fallback.
